---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import imgMain from "../assets/images/WEB_AnaAlbiol_EA-36.webp";
---

<Layout
    title="En Privado | Ana Albiol"
    description="En Privado. La newsletter de Ana Albiol. Lo que no sale en Instagram. Reflexiones, audios y contenido exclusivo."
    headerTheme="dark"
>
    <!-- Header is in Layout -->

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="newsletter-page-hero fade-up">
        <div class="container newsletter-hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-text-column">
                <h1>En Privado</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">
                    Lo que no sale en Instagram. Lo importante. Lo íntimo.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image-column">
                <div class="image-wrapper main-img">
                    <Image
                        src={imgMain}
                        alt="Ana Albiol"
                        class="hero-img"
                        widths={[300, 600, imgMain.width]}
                        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="section-padding">
        <div class="container fade-up">
            <div class="en-privado-content-layout">
                <div class="text-column">
                    <p class="main-text">
                        Para personas que aún valoran el largo y tendido.<br /><br />
                        Reflexiones, audios, detalles de cortesía, acceso anticipado a
                        las formaciones y directos.
                    </p>

                    <p class="schedule-text mt-4">
                        Los sábados, cada 15 días a las 9:00 am en tu bandeja de entrada.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="form-column">
                    <div class="form-container">
                        <h3>Lo que SÍ</h3>
                        <p>Contenido cuidado y personal.</p>
                        <hr style="margin: 2rem 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee;" />
                        <h3>Lo que NO</h3>
                        <p>
                            Te doy mi palabra de que no voy a bombardear tu correo
                            diariamente para que me tengas presente y poder venderte. 
                            <strong>Me horroriza. Y me niego.</strong>
                        </p>

                        <form class="newsletter-form mt-4" id="newsletter-form">
                            <input
                                type="email"
                                id="newsletter-email"
                                name="email"
                                autocomplete="email"
                                placeholder="Tu mejor email"
                                aria-label="Tu mejor email"
                                required
                                style="border: 1px solid #ddd;"
                            />
                            <button
                                type="submit"
                                class="btn btn-primary"
                                style="width: 100%;">Quiero entrar En Privado</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer is in Layout -->
</Layout>

<script>
    import { inView, animate } from "motion";

    // Form Handling
    const form = document.getElementById("newsletter-form");
    if (form) {
        form.addEventListener("submit", (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            const submitBtn = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]') as HTMLButtonElement | null;
            if (submitBtn) {
                submitBtn.setAttribute("disabled", "true");
                submitBtn.style.opacity = "0.6";
            }
            setTimeout(() => {
                window.location.href = "/gracias";
            }, 600);
        });
    }
</script>

<style>
    /* Newsletter Page Specific Styles */
    .newsletter-page-hero {
        background-color: var(--color-primary);
        color: white;
        padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
        text-align: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
    }

    .newsletter-hero-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 4rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    @media (min-width: 992px) {
        .newsletter-hero-grid {
            flex-direction: row;
            text-align: left;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .hero-text-column {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .hero-image-column {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            position: relative;
        }
    }

    .newsletter-page-hero h1 {
        color: white;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .newsletter-page-hero .subtitle {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
        max-width: 600px;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .hero-image-column {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-end;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .main-img {
        width: 250px;
        height: 350px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .main-img {
            width: 300px;
            height: 420px;
        }
    }

    .hero-img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* New Grid Layout for Content */
    .en-privado-content-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: start;
        text-align: left;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .text-column .main-text {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .text-column .schedule-text {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 992px) {
        .en-privado-content-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }
    }

    .form-container {
        background: white;
        padding: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    .newsletter-form {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .newsletter-form input {
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        font-family: var(--font-body);
    }
</style>
